{"tid":1964442,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"歐洲封關阻廁紙紙漿運送 廠商：供應延誤數天足以令生產線停止","createTime":"2020-04-08T22:00:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T23:33:52.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a0572eedc871c40f9bc01520c104d541cf2e6c98","tid":1964442,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T22:00:04.000Z","msg":"受武漢肺炎疫情影響，多國曾經出現搶購廁紙潮。如今歐洲多國實施封關，全球大型廁紙生產商表示運送的確有延誤，增加了時間及金錢成本。<br />\n<br />\n全球對廁紙需求大增，雖然各品牌暫時仍有足夠庫存，但也要加快生產應對要延長隔離期的最壞情況。挪威、德國及西班牙等歐洲國家在三月封關禁止不必要出行，雖然貨物仍可通過，但通關效率減慢導致延誤。廁紙原材料生產商、芬蘭的「Mets&auml; Fibre」及瑞典的「S&ouml;dra Cell International」表示，盛載紙漿的貨車在歐洲已塞車數小時甚至數天。供應稍為延誤數天足以令生產線停止，增加時間及金錢成本。<br />\n「Mets&auml; Fibre」銷售負責人哈馬拉（Ari Harmaala）說：「正常情況你不需要擔心交通。是否準時？是否送出？是否在貨櫃上？我們要用更多時間溝通去減少風險。」原材料生產商正招募更多司機應付需求，但疫情下不少司機擔心感染武漢肺炎而離職，部份生產商亦轉用鐵路運貨。<br />\n<br />\n日用品生產商寶潔公司（P&amp;G）表示，會以「最快速度」生產及運送廁紙到零售商，金佰利集團（Kimberly-Clark）也在加快生產並重新分配庫存以滿足大量需求，但兩間公司沒有評論供應鏈是否受阻。瑞典的愛適瑞（Essity）表示運送有延誤，但目前仍有足夠紙漿。哈馬拉說：「現在是時候做更多廁紙了－－我們確保要生產及運送最多的紙漿。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/zdkvscPQKNqPGNOtxO5O7kDr9OM=/802x445/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/G5SMAQIADELGGVU24HUOXVLCF4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FzdkvscPQKNqPGNOtxO5O7kDr9OM%3D%2F802x445%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FG5SMAQIADELGGVU24HUOXVLCF4.jpg&h=13b35adb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200408/BYF7UPN4RCB6CILUR7RZK3IG4Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200408%2FBYF7UPN4RCB6CILUR7RZK3IG4Y%2F&d=5ySQsq589lR7QRkangxGbhZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=3e4befe1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200408%2FBYF7UPN4RCB6CILUR7RZK3IG4Y%2F&h=b84464de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200408/BYF7UPN4RCB6CILUR7RZK3IG4Y/</a>"},{"pid":"05b85618362b05538f7cbb112de927e57dc24439","tid":1964442,"uid":186264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T22:29:15.000Z","msg":"德國家下廁紙已經無人買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efde46e3085354f8bebd954ae6a8cc2c76bcbf4e","tid":1964442,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T22:41:52.000Z","msg":"又炒過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1ee3f0fd921d209436567ae2362d09a2c7c69c0","tid":1964442,"uid":105924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05b85618362b05538f7cbb112de927e57dc24439","tid":1964442,"uid":186264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T22:29:15.000Z","msg":"德國家下廁紙已經無人買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T23:18:27.000Z","msg":"係，rewe啲廁紙而家多到仆街都無人問津 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e0496fd1c73b22cdf5973b1a07c0b2cc09db179","tid":1964442,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05b85618362b05538f7cbb112de927e57dc24439","tid":1964442,"uid":186264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T22:29:15.000Z","msg":"德國家下廁紙已經無人買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T23:33:52.000Z","msg":"香港都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}